Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然向我銀之鍊金術師朱利歐·科曼契挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的膽量值得稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只是擦到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只擦到一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺 您回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫張梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}東方的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次倒在路邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的主人 尤基大人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果好了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快點離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來治療傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是流傳於清國的鍊丹術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清國？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一個人穿越了東邊的大沙漠來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個人和一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻是指那個小東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 它叫小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鍊丹術吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探索流動於大地的力量——龍脈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且運用它的法術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個刺青結合了我國鍊丹術的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥不僅研究了鍊丹術 還研究了鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個刺青就是研究的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥是個非常優秀的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷也治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能毫無牽掛地去中央都市了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 馬上就準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不是叫妳快點離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說的不老不死什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的 我就是為此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 小鬼就要像個小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鍊丹術是無法實現不老不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是鍊金術的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必須去拜見傳說中的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮加金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的大衣 颯爽地披在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華麗地拯救人們的天才鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華·愛力克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 黑色疾風號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚一個人走路可是很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會被我剁碎手巴利襲擊的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼沒有反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為認識一個類似的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似？是叫阿爾馮斯什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識阿爾馮斯君？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那傢伙的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到第五研究所和製造石頭有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 說不定和軍隊上層也有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及名叫拉斯多和恩維的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們把你變成這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是研究人員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們強制把我的靈魂拖了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果調查那些研究者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能查出下令做研究的人是什麼來歷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也被作為石頭的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都沒有剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封口兼做材料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點都不浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否已經沒有必要再製造石頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後再問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個多月前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央都市的電話亭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害了一個軍隊將校的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙被切開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 溫莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳今天心情愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德 阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃現在都在認真工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄了偷盜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在靠修理房頂之類的工作來生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有 就是稍微繞了點遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是逐漸地進展吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 緊急處理完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在零件不夠 先這樣將就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就調集過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們隨便走走打發時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡只有機械鎧店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 撿了隻貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說要請你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼小氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許說「小」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在異國遇見的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常難得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在異國？你是外國人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 從清國來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指那個東邊的大國？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越沙漠真是非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要走這種路線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想看看克塞魯克塞斯遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克塞魯克塞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那裡什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要調查點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這個國家也是為了調查鍊丹術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊丹術？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家叫它鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的國家叫它鍊丹術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在醫學方面的頂尖技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的國情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡大多用於軍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也和南邊的阿耶魯戈 西邊的古雷達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在國境線附近總是有小衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方也是有大國德拉古馬存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說締結了互不侵犯條約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為布里克斯山擋在中間而不攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係也很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個危險的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鍊金術廣泛用於軍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是現在的大總統布拉德雷上任以後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們也很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有頂尖醫學水平的鍊丹術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你們是鍊金術師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的弟弟 阿爾馮斯·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細地說說鍊丹術的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是鍊丹術師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是術師來調查什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會不會知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常想要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來知道些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想用賢者之石做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它獲得不老不死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊 說什麼不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何 我可不覺得這是有求於人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要反抗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙會輕功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清國的體術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起師傅來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 追加甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼賢者之石 不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就打起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個狐狸眼混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 在我罵那個狐狸眼混蛋之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 帕妮孃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 基本上猜得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 帕妮孃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺不到那個鎧甲裡有活人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得增加人數就有辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下就這點水平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫麟的混蛋也就這點程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 這傢伙在主人被辱駡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就失去冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊變得單純而且動作也大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼差不多讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是義肢內藏炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不能輕視這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的話 也就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊丹術？居然不用陣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…哥哥也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被麟大人罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大街上居然用這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換了其他人的話 早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 自己把手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候經常追兔子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱可是我的拿手好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 居然像沒事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 做我的部下統治一個國家如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回清…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們居然把城市弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我賠償
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯錢拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯錢和賠償由這小子和他的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說這個國家的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 給我站住 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘了 說是修好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在這副樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 哥哥 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要鍊成陣就能鍊成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為真理的記憶恢復了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（天平左：鍊金水平 哥哥的威嚴）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（天平右：身高）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（背景字：哥哥的威嚴）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60}（背景字：哥哥的威嚴）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好意思喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過份 我們明明是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那兩個人 我可是遇到了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會好好教訓他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩叫蘭芳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子叫胡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們家族世代侍奉我家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭飯吃的傢伙居然有兩個隨從
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 我也算是皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不都吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 因為太意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種倒在路邊向人蹭飯的傢伙居然是皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許說麟大人的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實一點都不顯得身份高貴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇子也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清國是由50個民族聚集起來組成的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由皇帝統治全國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 各民族領袖的女兒嫁給皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生下小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的皇帝有二十四位皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和十九位皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這其中的第十二位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四十三個孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會為了繼承權而產生糾紛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就面臨這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝的身體狀況非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個民族都為了攀上皇位而不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不老不死的方法為餌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攀上皇位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於賢者之石的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石不是發跡的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴我的話 就一直跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大街上好像出了亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以回來晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你總是 總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主沒必要給下面的人低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我低個頭就能解決的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算很便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可關係到姚族50萬人的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒空管這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次準備到哪裡去弄壞機械鎧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄壞為前提嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去中央都市調查點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去中央都市嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去 想去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休斯家道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 溫莉有工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也需要放鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 伽菲爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家就一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去中央都市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待 中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你不要跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是跟來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 還沒問過老爺的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦爾的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己的名字作為神賜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿懷自豪地稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是 老爺肯定也有個非常自豪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把名字捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是有去無回的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就捨棄全部神賜之物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中充滿對再會的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到中央都市的愛德等人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接他們的是悲傷的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 黑暗選出了新的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第16話 戰友的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出行的男人心中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光明還是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:23.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}純白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:29.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:41.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:47.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:49.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:59.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:01.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:06.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:13.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:16.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:22.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:31.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:43.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:34.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:38.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:45.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這樣描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:50.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上塗鴉的花也會搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:56.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:58.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫長的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去與獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:09.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:17.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也好  痛苦也好  都將化為恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:23.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃照亮明天的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:28.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起小手  兩個人一起創造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:33.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜尋星塵與光芒四射的永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:39.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 那天也許還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:45.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季節依然在不斷地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:49.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有點迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:53.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}請讓我維持到永遠


